Thumbs.db

# Env / secrets
.env
.env.*
!.env.example
!.env.prod.example
# Bare `env` / `env.*` reference files at the repo root — kept local; the
# canonical pattern is `.env` / `.env.example` (above). A real Brain `env`
# file holds live API + EVM keys and must NOT be committed even by accident.
/env
/env.*
!/.env.example
secrets/
*.pem
*.key
!**/fixtures/**/*.key

